<dd><b>NOTE</b>: The 10 objecting Congressmen against Lee's citizenship resolution argued it should include <a href="/wiki/Draft_dodgers#Draft_dodging_and_the_Vietnam_War" title="Draft dodgers" class="mw-redirect">amnesty for Vietham war draft dodgers (subsequently granted in 1977</a>).</dd>
</dl>
